import { BrowserRouter, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

import Home from '../pages/Home/Home'
import Introduction from '../pages/Introduction/Introduction'

export default function Routers() {
    return (
        <BrowserRouter>
            <Switch>
                <Route path="/">
                    <Home />
                </Route>
                <Route path="/Introduction">
                    <Introduction />
                </Route>
            </Switch>
        </BrowserRouter>
    )
}
